descriptionHtml:
Download this free app to stay informed and up to date with service & location information, audio & video messages from our Senior Pastor James Green, links to our live stream, as well as to submit prayer requests, view upcoming events, give online, join a life group & more!

Champion Life Centre, also known as CLC Spring, is located in Spring, TX just north of the city of Houston and south of The Woodlands.

Champion Life Centre exists to be the church for the unchurched and to lead people into a growing relationship with Christ.

Follow us on Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram: clcspring

For more information on our church, please visit our website at: http://clcspring.org

The Champion Life Centre app was developed with the Subsplash App Platform.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.
